OL,7,FA grieving daughter has described how
OL,8,Fher bank handed her a #1 coin instead
OL,9,Fof a loan after her family was left
OL,10,Fdestitute when her father died from .
OL,12,FNeil Kerr, a former civil servant,
OL,13,Fcontracted HIV and hepatitis C from
OL,14,Finfected blood products, which were
OL,15,Fgiven to him to treat his haemophilia
OL,16,F- a blood clotting disorder.
