OL,4,Cafter our father's death from infected
OL,5,Cblood'
OL,7,FAfter his death, his family were
OL,8,Fturfed out of their home, their car
OL,9,Fwas repossessed and they did not know
OL,10,Fwhere their next meal was going to
OL,11,Fcome from.
OL,13,FHis daughter, Lisa Nelson, described
OL,14,Fhow she went to the bank to ask for a
OL,15,Floan and was only given a #1 coin.
OL,17,F"I remember going to the bank one day
OL,18,Fand just begging for help. And they
OL,19,Fhanded me a pound coin," she said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
