OL,5,Cblood'
OL,7,F"He was only 42 when he passed. I'm
OL,8,Fnow older than my dad ever got to be
OL,9,Fwhich is scary."
OL,11,FMr Kerr had severe haemophilia type A
OL,12,Fand was co-infected with HIV and
OL,13,Fhepatitis C during his treatment.
OL,15,FMs Nelson was 21 when her father died
OL,16,Ffrom Aids in 2000.
OL,18,F"His death was gruesome - we managed
OL,19,Fto shield my brother and my sister -
OL,20,Fthey were younger than me at the
OL,21,Ftime," she said.
