OL,7,F"We brought them up when we knew it
OL,8,Fwas a few hours away... there was so
OL,9,Fmuch blood - from his eyes, his ears,
OL,10,Fhis mouth, his throat, it was just
OL,11,Fhorrendous."
OL,13,FShe described how a couple of months
OL,14,Flater, Mr Kerr's death money stopped
OL,15,Fcoming in to the family.
