OL,7,F"After dad passed we lost our home,
OL,8,Fthe car was repossessed, there were
OL,9,Fjust days where we didn't have food or
OL,10,Fmoney," said Ms Nelson, who now works
OL,11,Fas a manager for the Northern Ireland
OL,12,Fcardiology network.
OL,14,F"I don't even know how we got through
OL,15,Fit when I look back to it now. It was
OL,16,Fhorrendous, a very dark time.
OL,18,F"There were constant debt collector
OL,19,Fcalls and it was myself that dealt
OL,20,Fwith those and to deal with the house
OL,21,Fbecause my mum just couldn't.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/13
