OL,7,FAsked about compensation for those
OL,8,Faffected by the scandal, she said:
OL,9,F"There are people in our position
OL,10,Fright now and that person is still
OL,11,Falive and I'm sure they are worried
OL,12,Fsick about what is going to happen to
OL,13,Ftheir families too.
OL,15,F"Dad wasn't entitled to life insurance
OL,16,Fwhich is why we ended up the way we
OL,17,Fwere.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/13
