OL,5,Cblood'
OL,7,F"The majority of these people aren't
OL,8,Fentitled to life insurance as a
OL,9,Fresult, so when they go how are they
OL,10,Fdoing to make sure their families are
OL,11,FOK?
OL,13,F"That should be the last thing someone
OL,14,Fis thinking about when they are coming
OL,15,Fto the end of their life, especially
OL,16,Fwhen this isn't their fault - they're
OL,17,Fsick through for something that was
OL,18,Fdone to them, not the the luck of the
OL,19,Fdraw, this is from something that had
OL,20,Fbeen given to them.
