OL,5,Cblood'
OL,7,F"Compensation is not just about money,
OL,8,Fits recognition of the people who have
OL,9,Fdied, the trauma that they had to go
OL,10,Fthrough, it's justice.
OL,12,F"It is having to get your begging bowl
OL,13,Fout which is not dignified when these
OL,14,Fpeople are sick, it's not their fault
OL,15,Fthey are sick, they're just trying to
OL,16,Fmake ends meet.
OL,18,F"It's hard enough when your health is
OL,19,Fdeclining without financial burdens
OL,20,Fbeing put on you.
