OL,9,Fthrough. And it just sickens me that
OL,10,Fit is not."
OL,12,FTens of thousands of people were
OL,13,Finfected with contaminated blood or
OL,14,Fblood products between the 1970s and
OL,15,Fearly 1990s.
OL,17,FThe scandal - dubbed the worst
OL,18,Ftreatment disaster in the history of
OL,19,Fthe NHS - has been the subject of the
OL,20,Fbiggest ever public inquiry in the UK.
